## 6Ô∏è‚É£ How It Works (Step-by-Step Guide)

**Title:** Start in under 30 seconds

1. Install ActSMS on Android 10+
2. Grant SMS read permission (clear explanation shown)
3. Receive a transactional SMS
4. ActSMS detects intent and extracts key data
5. A reminder/task/alert is auto-created
6. You can accept, snooze, or ignore ‚Äî the app learns

